data.description: Location location ( $30K Price adjustment) Hurry !!! Pride of ownership, one of the best known Split level spacious home on the block . lots of curves and Curb appeals,  3 level . Well maintained, professionally  cared landscape .  Recently installed Stainless steel appliances.  Enjoy lovely Sun filled Family room with Fireplace,  Bay window , skylight and so many dim-able recess lights  .  5 bedrooms , 3 full bathroom,  Walkout basement with private side entrance ,with 2 bedroom and full bath,, wet bar or a kitchenette . Charming addition ( studio) with cherry laminate wood flooring  with its own private rear entrance and interior  French glass door access at dinning room/ main level with 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom . Addition could be great kids play room or guest sitting room or rental studio.  Great backyard with craftsman  porched workshop  and a shed.
